The paper proposes a deep feedforward neural network that learns from algebraic reasoning examples produced by humans and imitates human intelligence of problem solving. This work involves machine learning, artificial intelligence, and natural language processing, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CL, and cs.CV. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
